author: wn.com
title: Obama says response to shootings has become too routine in wake of Oregon college shooting
text: A visibly frustrated President Obama said Thursday that thoughts and prayers are no longer enough as Americans respond to another deadly school shooting, and he challenged voters wanting to deal with the problem to vote for elected officials who will do something. ...
